	   <tr><td colspan=2>We were testing these gloves , fbss, and hand wraps.   Sporali gloves and fbss have same haste - hand wraps were a bit faster tho.   try to kill a spawn that stays the same lvl at every pop then get a stop watch and watch in other view to see ur attack and hits,  then scroll back and see in text how many times u hit --- Sporali and Fbss hit the same but gloves have lil ac .  Hand Wraps were faster by bout 8- 10 persent and had saves and ac So hand wraps Rock.   Fbss andd Sporali were the same tho fbss is lil over rated.   I would have to say Gloves are better because of the ac even if its just a small amount.  AC = #1 in the game.  If you have lots of AC and HP items you will out live the ones who consentrate on wis int or str : )   Happy Hunting  *sorry if spelling is bad its 12:30am /yawn.  BTW we tried all 3 of these haste items and a haste item forgot name from Seb But the one from Seb was just to good to compare to the other 3 )   /bye  <br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
