	   <tr><td colspan=2>first off, the minimum delay on ANY weapon is 11.  or 1.1 seconds.  It's coded into everquest.  you cannot hit any faster than 11.  I've heard roumors of people's delay down to 10, but only possible way is because of a slight bit of lag.  <br>if you want to figure out the haste, make a chatlog.txt while using a certain haste item, then try it again without the haste item.  That is the only way to really figure out how much faster you really are.  Untill VI spits out a formulat that they say is the formula for haste, forget tryin to figure it out. <br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
