	   <tr><td colspan=2>Ok one last quick lesson on haste =).  Haste % is actually an increase in damage output.  So 100% haste would mean 100% more damage, or twice as much.  Since the increase in damage is done by makign you swing faster 100%haste means you have half the original delay thus hitting twice as much and having double the average damage output.  The formulas peopel wrote were right (I think) but that is why it works liek it does.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
