<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=99305663488541></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f99305663488541><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=item.html?item=6019&mid=99305663488541>haste calc</a> <a id=fs8 href=item.html?item=6019&mid=99305663488541#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Wed, Jun 20th 1:03 PM 2001</td>
	   <td id=headerrow align=right><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Default<span id=notbold>[2.00]</span></td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=2>Hasted Weapon Delay = ( 1 /(1+ (haste item % + Haste spell%)) ) * Old Weapon Delay.<br><br>So at 10 % haste. on a 40 delay weapon. the new delay would be<br><br>HWD = (1 / (1 + (.10))) * 40 = 36.36<br><br>The max haste you can get is 100% So max haste = 1/1+1 = 1/2 old delay.<br><br>At max haste your 40 delay weapon will become a 20 delay weapon.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
